Text: Om du har mer av Kaizers så får du hemskt gärna lägga ut det :)
Yeah! Seed it! We need kaizers!!!

Believe it or not, but I did actually sing in that childrens choir. It consisted of two independent choirs, Sølvguttene and Bøler Girls Choir, and I was part of the group from Sølvguttene. It was one of the most interesting and fun things I have ever done.
